  <brief_title>Rehabilitation of Young Patients With Rheumatic Diseases in a Warm Climate</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Rehabilitation of Young Patients With Rheumatic Diseases in a Warm Climate. A Pilot Randomised Controlled Trial</official_title>
