    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Inflammatory rheumatic disease

          -  Self reliant in daily life

        Exclusion Criteria:

        - conditions that might influence ability to fly to Spain and participate in
        rehabilitation in warm climate (Unstable heart disease, Serious lung disease, Chronic open
        ulcers, Serious mental health conditions, alcohol or drug addiction, Intolerant of sun and
        heat)
